  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a dynamic scene of several brown pelicans soaring in the sky above a busy port. Below, a sprawling container yard filled with rows of colorful shipping containers dominates the mid-ground, punctuated by the towering cranes used for loading and unloading cargo. The cranes are white and grey, their structures creating a geometric pattern against the stacks of containers. In the distant background, a hazy blue and green landscape of rolling hills and buildings rises, suggesting an urban or suburban area. The pelicans are silhouetted against the bright sky, adding a sense of freedom and movement to the industrial setting.",
